    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust on the wheel arches, several large dents, and peeling paint across the hood and roof. Mechanically, the engine runs but requires immediate attention due to a persistent oil leak and a failing transmission that slips between gears. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics, including the radio and air conditioning. Please expect to invest significant time and money to get this vehicle back into reliable shape.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
